---
// Contact form + Company info section (Web3Forms)
---

<section id="contact" class="reveal">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <span class="text-sm text-primary font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Contact</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">無料でご相談ください</h2>
      <p class="text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">海外営業に関するお悩みをお気軽にご相談ください。担当者が1営業日以内にご連絡いたします。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Form -->
      <div>
        <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-5">
          <input type="hidden" name="access_key" value="afd75ef5-c9e9-4be6-9f02-2b2d6a415434" />
          <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="【海外セールスくん】お問い合わせ" />
          <input type="hidden" name="from_name" value="海外セールスくん" />
          <input type="checkbox" name="botcheck" class="hidden" />

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">お問い合わせ種別</label>
            <select name="inquiry_type" required class="w-full border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none">
              <option value="">選択してください</option>
              <option value="consultation">無料相談</option>
              <option value="document">資料請求</option>
              <option value="estimate">見積もり依頼</option>
              <option value="other">その他</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">会社名 <span class="text-primary">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" name="company" required placeholder="例: 株式会社サンプル" class="w-full border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">お名前 <span class="text-primary">*</span></label>
            <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="例: 山田 太郎" class="w-full border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">メールアドレス <span class="text-primary">*</span></label>
            <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="example@company.co.jp" class="w-full border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">電話番号</label>
            <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="090-XXXX-XXXX" class="w-full border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-medium mb-1">ご相談内容</label>
            <textarea name="message" rows="4" placeholder="海外営業に関するご相談内容をお書きください" class="w-full border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary outline-none resize-vertical"></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors text-lg shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">
            送信する
          </button>

          <p class="text-xs text-muted text-center">
            送信いただいた情報は<a href="/privacy" class="underline">プライバシーポリシー</a>に基づき適切に管理します。
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <!-- Company info -->
      <div>
        <div class="bg-bg-alt rounded-xl p-8 mb-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">運営会社</h3>
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-border">
                <td class="py-3 text-muted w-28">会社名</td>
                <td class="py-3">株式会社Albaly<br /><span class="text-muted text-xs">Albaly Group Co., Ltd.</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border">
                <td class="py-3 text-muted">代表者</td>
                <td class="py-3">木本 彰宏</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border">
                <td class="py-3 text-muted">設立</td>
                <td class="py-3">2021年（タイ法人）<br />2024年（日本法人）</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border">
                <td class="py-3 text-muted">拠点</td>
                <td class="py-3">
                  タイ（バンコク）<br />
                  日本（福岡県）
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-border">
                <td class="py-3 text-muted">従業員数</td>
                <td class="py-3">約30名</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-3 text-muted">メール</td>
                <td class="py-3">
                  <a href="mailto:corporate_sales@albaly.jp" class="text-primary underline">
                    corporate_sales@albaly.jp
                  </a>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-primary-light rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-2">お急ぎの方はこちら</p>
          <a href="tel:0661318773" class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">
            066-131-8773
          </a>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">平日 9:00〜18:00（タイ時間）</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
